what people would make of it.

635
01:10:59,109 --> 01:11:02,227
He must have realized how it would
compromise you.

636
01:11:02,885 --> 01:11:04,950
Unless it was done in innocence.

637
01:11:05,189 --> 01:11:07,017
The fatherly gesture?

638
01:11:08,301 --> 01:11:10,900
He was like a father to you,
wasn't he?

639
01:11:11,169 --> 01:11:12,732
A guardian.

640
01:11:19,375 --> 01:11:21,600
