for a word from you.

677
01:14:55,991 --> 01:14:56,995
Georges.

678
01:14:57,258 --> 01:15:00,327
My beautiful boy.
- Don't call me that!

679
01:15:08,132 --> 01:15:09,753
They're not for you.

680
01:15:11,050 --> 01:15:13,522
