to take Morocco.

702
01:16:37,278 --> 01:16:38,489
Virginia.

703
01:16:38,780 --> 01:16:40,839
The new government came to power,

704
01:16:41,059 --> 01:16:43,042
I brought them to power,

705
01:16:43,330 --> 01:16:45,047
