706
01:16:45,270 --> 01:16:47,315
That's the whole point.

707
01:16:47,716 --> 01:16:49,116
Don't you see?

708
01:16:49,973 --> 01:16:51,961
No one's expecting it.

709
01:16:52,234 --> 01:16:53,817
My husband and Laroche have been hatching

710
01:16:53,820 --> 01:16:56,051
this plan for a long time.

711
01:16:56,304 --> 01:16:59,107
The first troops sail tonight.

712
01:16:59,679 --> 01:17:01,661
Tonight?

713
01:17:02,176 --> 01:17:04,274
But they would have included me.

714
01:17:05,425 --> 01:17:06,837
They don't trust you.

715
01:17:07,072 --> 01:17:09,156
They think you're too impulsive.

716
01:17:09,392 --> 01:17:12,427
Too greedy, they say.
Not used to having money.

717
01:17:12,430 --> 01:17:15,827
They think that you'll give them away.

718
01:17:16,357 --> 01:17:20,138
They think I'm too greedy?
- They don't know you as I do.

719
01:17:20,540 --> 01:17:24,250
Over the past few weeks,
they've bought the entire Moroccan loan.

720
01:17:24,400 --> 01:17:28,000
They've bought every copper mine in Morocco.
Every last one.

721
01:17:28,298 --> 01:17:31,587
They stand to make 70 million apiece.

722
01:17:34,289 --> 01:17:36,110
