Madame Duroy de Contel.

813
01:27:13,293 --> 01:27:16,906
I have found you here in a place
that is not your home.

814
01:27:16,941 --> 01:27:19,352
With Mr. Francaise Laroche.

815
01:27:19,640 --> 01:27:22,451
Do you admit to this man
as your lover?

816
01:27:22,734 --> 01:27:24,135
I admit it.

817
01:27:25,181 --> 01:27:28,389
Madame I have no choice
but to charge you with adultery.

818
01:27:28,821 --> 01:27:31,648
Is there anything you wish to say?
- No.

819
01:27:31,921 --> 01:27:33,364
Let's leave her in peace.

820
01:27:33,626 --> 01:27:35,843
We have no further business here.

821
01:27:38,334 --> 01:27:39,863
What should I do?

822
01:27:40,142 --> 01:27:41,504
Should I go?

823
01:27:41,539 --> 01:27:42,867
No, stay.

824
01:27:43,156 --> 01:27:45,290
Finish, if you like.

825
01:27:53,205 --> 01:27:54,325
Well,

826
01:27:55,210 --> 01:27:58,000
you'll hear from my lawyer
in a few days.

827
01:28:00,014 --> 01:28:02,242
Good-bye, Georges.

828
01:28:03,229 --> 01:28:05,460
Good-bye.

829
01:28:23,924 --> 01:28:27,983
I couldn't get away!
They were shouting and screaming on and on.

830
01:28:28,330 --> 01:28:32,217
My mum wouldn't stop crying and wailing,
she was like a mad woman.

831
01:28:34,084 --> 01:28:37,007
I wish I could see their faces
when they find me gone!

832
01:28:37,010 --> 01:28:38,915
Papa will turn blue.

833
01:28:58,991 --> 01:29:01,067
We'll need two rooms.

834
01:29:10,964 --> 01:29:13,747
Good night, Suzanne.
- But...

835
01:29:16,882 --> 01:29:19,702
I need a good-night kiss.

836
01:29:25,382 --> 01:29:27,130
You should get some sleep.

837
01:29:27,453 --> 01:29:30,459
But I...
- Get some sleep.

838
01:29:52,786 --> 01:29:53,908
Papa.

839
01:29:55,417 --> 01:29:56,539
Maman.

840
01:30:12,086 --> 01:30:15,262
He will not marry her.
- I should have seen it coming.

841
01:30:15,264 --> 01:30:18,553
He will not marry her!

842
01:30:18,839 --> 01:30:22,142
I will not...
Stop it!

843
01:30:22,157 --> 01:30:24,407
He will marry her!

844
01:30:24,410 --> 01:30:26,771
He must marry her!

845
01:30:27,034 --> 01:30:29,669
And you will accept it, Virginia!

846
01:30:29,754 --> 01:30:31,987
This is as much your doing
as it is mine!

847
01:30:32,063 --> 01:30:33,294
My doing?

848
01:30:33,502 --> 01:30:37,721
Your infatuation for him
infected my daughter!

849
01:30:38,288 --> 01:30:41,809
He will marry her,
and I will be glad of it.

850
01:30:41,893 --> 01:30:45,372
What more can a father wish for,
than to see his daughter

851
01:30:45,375 --> 01:30:48,100
with a man he can respect?

852
01:31:03,603 --> 01:31:06,000
She's only a child.

853
01:31:07,429 --> 01:31:09,680
Do you love her?
- No.

854
01:31:13,263 --> 01:31:15,360
She's of no interest to me.

855
01:31:17,229 --> 01:31:19,100
Poor little Suzanne.

856
01:31:19,421 --> 01:31:21,300
Suzanne's her father.

857
01:31:21,546 --> 01:31:23,880
Just some perfect miniature.

858
01:31:24,353 --> 01:31:28,000
You've ruined her.
I haven't. I'm going to marry her.

859
01:31:30,095 --> 01:31:32,076
Did you sleep with her?

860
01:31:33,688 --> 01:31:34,809
No.

861
01:31:35,488 --> 01:31:37,211
You didn't sleep with her.

862
01:31:37,435 --> 01:31:38,761
I didn't touch her.

863
01:31:38,999 --> 01:31:40,559
I didn't need to.

864
01:31:40,843 --> 01:31:43,300
It was enough for people
to think I had.

865
01:31:43,960 --> 01:31:46,081
I don't know you at all.

866
01:31:46,948 --> 01:31:48,069
You do.

867
01:31:48,302 --> 01:31:49,769
Oh, do I?

868
01:31:52,026 --> 01:31:54,100
He planned it.

869
01:31:55,098 --> 01:31:57,000
You planned it!

870
01:31:58,448 --> 01:32:00,453
You've ruined Laroche.

871
01:32:00,723 --> 01:32:03,361
You humiliated Madeleine.

872
01:32:03,622 --> 01:32:06,000
You humiliated her!

873
01:32:06,724 --> 01:32:09,000
All, so you could take Suzanne.

874
01:32:09,283 --> 01:32:10,657
Suzanne chose me because I was

875
01:32:10,659 --> 01:32:12,532
the only one she wasn't
allowed to have.

876
01:32:12,766 --> 01:32:13,888
And me?

877
01:32:14,099 --> 01:32:17,645
Did you ever think,
how this would hurt me?

878
01:32:17,859 --> 01:32:20,460
It has nothing to do with you.

879
01:32:21,175 --> 01:32:23,293
Then why am I in pain?

880
01:32:23,299 --> 01:32:24,847
I don't know.

881
01:32:25,115 --> 01:32:27,327
You didn't even tell me yourself.

882
01:32:27,441 --> 01:32:30,512
I had to hear it from my husband.

883
01:32:31,007 --> 01:32:32,822
You think I'll forgive you anything.

884
01:32:32,832 --> 01:32:35,942
I will not be stopped, Clotilde.

885
01:32:36,255 --> 01:32:38,250
I will marry her.

886
01:32:40,509 --> 01:32:42,947
You're just one of them, after all.

887
01:32:45,808 --> 01:32:47,339
Just another,

888
01:32:47,942 --> 01:32:50,627
selfish, brutal man.

889
01:32:51,172 --> 01:32:53,809
Just another thief.

890
01:32:54,124 --> 01:32:57,166
It's not enough to be loved, is it?

891
01:32:57,402 --> 01:33:00,000
Oh, you must be a king!

892
01:33:00,854 --> 01:33:01,974
No.

893
01:33:04,498 --> 01:33:06,921
It's not enough to be loved.

894
01:33:07,166 --> 01:33:09,195
Even by you.

895
01:33:11,061 --> 01:33:14,200
I loved you when you had nothing.

896
01:33:14,769 --> 01:33:18,467
I don't understand
why you must be so proud.

897
01:33:21,009 --> 01:33:24,637
I don't understand.
- It's because you've never been poor.

898
01:33:25,241 --> 01:33:29,280
Trying to scrape out some miserable
scrap of an existence!

899
01:33:31,220 --> 01:33:33,774
I can't live like that.

900
01:33:34,555 --> 01:33:36,319
Like my father.

901
01:33:38,148 --> 01:33:40,302
Working to the bone,

902
01:33:40,936 --> 01:33:43,562
and then down on his knees,
every week,

903
01:33:44,537 --> 01:33:47,782
praying to God that the next
life will be better.

904
01:33:49,879 --> 01:33:52,440
Well, there is no next life.

905
01:33:53,480 --> 01:33:54,750
The flesh,

906
01:33:55,001 --> 01:33:57,022
it rots in the earth.

907
01:33:57,759 --> 01:34:00,007
It rots.

908
01:34:02,016 --> 01:34:05,124
I have seen a man die.

909
01:34:05,496 --> 01:34:09,606
And I am going to live.

910
01:34:11,718 --> 01:34:14,300
It's so clear to me.

911
01:34:18,456 --> 01:34:21,000
I thought you'd understand.

